你這段 SQL 有幾個問題：

1. WITH 不能直接寫在 IN (...) 裡面。
2. 最後一句：

SELECT CustomerNo,IsSARFiled FROM BANCS_SK_CUST_INFO

看起來不對，因為你前面都在用 TS_CUST_ID，而且 BANCS_SK_CUST_INFO 應該沒有 IsSARFiled 欄位。

⸻

如果你的驗證邏輯是：

Step 1

找出

只有 FLG=1
沒有 FLG=2、3

的 TS_CUST_ID

Step 2

確認這些客戶在 VERIFY 的 BSA_SUB_CUST_FACT 裡 IsSARFiled=1

Step 3

查看這些客戶在來源資料(SK/NP)的 SAR 狀態是否也是 1

那我建議直接做成比對表：

WITH CUST_LIST AS
(
    SELECT TS_CUST_ID
    FROM BANCS_SK_CUST_INFO
    WHERE CUST_RE_NO_FLG = '1'
    EXCEPT
    SELECT TS_CUST_ID
    FROM BANCS_SK_CUST_INFO
    WHERE CUST_RE_NO_FLG IN ('2','3')
)
SELECT
    c.TS_CUST_ID,
    v.IsSARFiled AS VERIFY_IsSARFiled
FROM CUST_LIST c
JOIN VERIFY..BSA_SUB_CUST_FACT v
    ON c.TS_CUST_ID = v.CustomerNo
WHERE v.IsSARFiled = 1
ORDER BY c.TS_CUST_ID;

如果你要再跟來源 NP 的資料比：

WITH CUST_LIST AS
(
    SELECT TS_CUST_ID
    FROM BANCS_SK_CUST_INFO
    WHERE CUST_RE_NO_FLG = '1'
    EXCEPT
    SELECT TS_CUST_ID
    FROM BANCS_SK_CUST_INFO
    WHERE CUST_RE_NO_FLG IN ('2','3')
),
NP_RESULT AS
(
    SELECT
        b.TS_CUST_ID,
        MAX(CAST(ISNULL(n.IsSARFiled,0) AS INT)) AS NP_IsSARFiled
    FROM BANCS_SK_CUST_INFO b
    JOIN Customer_Migrate_buffer m
        ON b.SK_CUST_ID = m.CustomerNo
    JOIN Cust_NP_Migrate_buffer n
        ON m.CIF_KEY = n.CIF_KEY
    GROUP BY b.TS_CUST_ID
)
SELECT
    c.TS_CUST_ID,
    p.NP_IsSARFiled,
    v.IsSARFiled AS VERIFY_IsSARFiled,
    CASE
        WHEN p.NP_IsSARFiled = CAST(v.IsSARFiled AS INT)
        THEN 'Same'
        ELSE 'Different'
    END AS CompareResult
FROM CUST_LIST c
JOIN VERIFY..BSA_SUB_CUST_FACT v
    ON c.TS_CUST_ID = v.CustomerNo
LEFT JOIN NP_RESULT p
    ON c.TS_CUST_ID = p.TS_CUST_ID
WHERE v.IsSARFiled = 1
ORDER BY c.TS_CUST_ID;

